[03:35:09] [req:117] in en->ru: "You are protected by a durable carapace.\n\n+3 AV\n-2 DV\n+10 Heat Resistance\n+10 Cold Resistance\n+400 reputation with tortoises\nYou may tighten your carapace to receive double the AV bonus at a -2 DV penalty as long as you remain still....(truncated)"
